<p>into a Convalescent Home   4 of us shared a room here, they were nice rooms &amp; very cool the food here was of the very best   we had tennis courts &amp; sports grounds right handy while in the building there were any amount of fine bathrooms &amp; good reading &amp; writing rooms 2 or 3 pianos, &amp; 4 times weekly there was a fine picture show you could lean out of your window &amp; watch the pictures, every morning there would be a medical inspection &amp; those fit would be drafted out &amp; sent away to the detail camp at Giza,<br/>I had 2 pretty solid injections</p>
